'''Muhutukazi Marie Mediatrice''' ni umubyeyi w'umunyarwandakazi umenyerewe muri [[Filimi ya Seburikoko|filimi]] nyarwanda nka Kankwanzi mu runana, ukina [[Filimi ya Seburikoko|filimi]] zitadukanye kandi  akaba ari n'umwe mu bakinnyi b’ikinamico mu [[Rwanda]].

== UBUZIMA BWITE ==
'''Muhutukazi Marie Mediatrice''' [wavutse 1964] ni [[umugore]] tumenyereye kumazina ya Kankwanzi , yavukiye mu [[Kigali|uMujyi wa Kigali]], mu [[akarere ka Nyarugenge]]. Ni [[imfura]] mu bana batatu bavukana nawe. Mu buzima busanzwe ni [[Umubyeyi Sharifa|umubyeyi]] w’[[Umwana|abana]] babiri[umuhungu n’umukobwa] gusa ntiyagize amahirwe yo gusazana n’umugabo kuko batandukanye ubu buri wese akaba y'ibana ariko by’umwihariko  Marie Médiatrice akaba abana n’aba [[abana]] be bombi. Mu amashuri yisumbuye yize Sicial.<ref>https://www.eachamps.rw/article/5604/Shira-amatsiko-kuri-Kankwanzi-ukinana-numukobwa-we-mu-Runana</ref> 

== IKINAMICO NA FILIMI ==
'''Muhutukazi Marie Mediatrice''' avuga ko yatangiye kwiyumvamo impano akiri muto gusa akaza kugira amahirwe yo gutangira gukina ikinamico ku mugaragaro mu 1988 ubwo yari afite [[Umwaka|imyaka]] 24 y’amavuko.Yagize ati”Natangiye [[Umuhanzi Kamariza|ubuhanzi]] bw’ikinamico mu 1988. Ni impano nari mfite kuko natangiye kuyiyumvamo nkiri [[umwana]], nyuma ya [[Jenoside mu Rwanda|Jenosid]]<nowiki/>e  yakorewe [[Abatutsi]] anjya mu itorero rya Mashirika,  mu 1998  nabwo Urunana ruza gushaka abakinnyi ngiyeyo ndatsinda ninjiramo gutyo.”<ref>https://umuryango.rw/ad-restricted/article/ibyo-wamenya-kuri-kankwanzi-wamamaye-mu-ikinamico-urunana-ari-umugore-wa</ref> 

=== IZINA KANKWANZI ===
'''Muhutukazi Marie Mediatrice'''  nka '''Kankwanzi''' akigera mu ikinamico Urunana kwitwa iri zina yabanje kubyanga kubera ukuntu yari kujya akina ari [[umugore]] ugaragaza ubujiji bwinshi.Yagize ati”Mu Urunana bari bari gushaka abakinnyi 8, babanje gutoranye 16 ndatsinda, barongera batoranya abandi 8 nabo mbazamo. Bampaye umwanya wa '''Kankwanzi'''  ndawanga cyane, nkavuga nti’Ntabwo nakina ndi [[Ikigori|ikigoryi]] meze kuriya’ ariko umwanditsi ambwira ko ari nziza ngeze aho ndabyemera.” Yavuze ko hari amahugurwa yari amazemo iminsi bamubwira ko [[Umuhanzi Kamariza|umuhanzi]] mwiza nta mwanya atakina birangira yemeye gukina ari mu ishusho ya Kankwanzi w’umunyacyaro.Kankwanzi avuga ko bitewe n'uburyo akina ari [[umugore]] w'umuturage kandi w' hari abantu benshi baba bumva ko ari nako ateye mu [[ubuzima]] busanzwe, gusa ngo iyo bamubonye birabatungura.Yagize ati “Hari [[Umuturirwa (Waltheria)|umuntu]] wavuye mu [[Ubufaransa|Bufaransa]] w’umuzungukazi na we ukora biriya by’amakinamico, ambwira ko yumvaga ndi umunyacyaro cyane mfite ubujiji nka buriya mba ngaragaza. Na bamwe mu abanyamakuru ba BBC bigeze kuza mu [[Rwanda]] bambonye baratangara.”<ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/115359/kankwanzi-wa-bushombe-yahishuye-uko-yubatse-amazu-akuye-ubushobozi-mu-gukina-ikinamico-asa-115359.html</ref><ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/65608/ukuri-ku-makuru-ari-gucicikana-ko-umukinnyi-mu-ikinamico-uru-65608.html</ref>

=== IBYO AGEZEHO ===
'''Muhutukazi Marie Mediatrice'''  nka Kwankwanzi Kankwanzi yemeza ko Urunana rumaze kugira uruhare rukomeye mu [[Iterambere ry'umugore mu Rwanda|iterambere]] ry’[[Umuryango w’Abibumye|umuryango]] we, ndetse akaba yariyubakiye [[Inzu Ndangamurage ya Richard Kandt|inzu]] akubaka n’izindi zo gukodesha zimwinjiriza amafaranga buri [[ukwezi]]. Akina ikinamico abikomatanya na [[Filimi ya Seburikoko|filime]] ariko yemeza ko Urunana ari rwo rwamufashije cyane kuko [[Filimi ya Seburikoko|filime]] yagiye akina ari nkeya kandi zikaba zitanabamo amafaranga menshi.Yagize ati”Urunana rumaze kungeza kuri byinshi nabashije kwiyubakira [[Inzu Ndangamurage ya Richard Kandt|inzu]] y'i[[IFUMBIRE MVARUGANDA|icumbi]], narihiye [[abana]] [[Amashuri Makuru|amashuri]] nubaka n’andi mazu yo gukodesha byose kubera kurukomatanya no gukina [[Filimi ya Seburikoko|filime]] ariko navuga ko uruhare runini ari Urunana kuko muri [[Filimi ya Seburikoko|filime]] nta mafaranga arimo menshi.”Yakinnye muri [[Filimi ya Seburikoko|filime]] yitwa ‘[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kEFp4oWmHgc Haranira kubaho]’,<ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kEFp4oWmHgc</ref> ‘[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=as_xOjEopbY Zirara zishya]’<ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=as_xOjEopbY</ref>   n’izindi nyinshi ndetse by’umwihariko yananyuze muri [[SEBURIKOKO|Seburikoko]]  <ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kpwclR8RhbY</ref> ariko ntabwo akigaragaramo kuko mu mwanya yakinagamo yapfuye.<ref>https://umuryango.rw/ad-restricted/article/ibyo-wamenya-kuri-kankwanzi-wamamaye-mu-ikinamico-urunana-ari-umugore-wa</ref><ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i8_FHGO9iCE</ref>

=== IBYO AKUNDA ===
'''Muhutukazi Marie Mediatrice''' Avuga ko akunda cyane abahanzi bo ha mbere biganjemo Fredéric Francois, George Moustaki, Nana Mouskouri n’abandi. Ati ‘bariya bahanzi baririmba [[Indirimbo y’igihugu|indirimbo]] zituje z[[Igifaransa|’igifaransa]] zo ha mbere ndazikunda cyane.’Mu bahanzi bo mu [[Rwanda]] b’ubu avuga ko azi Amag The Black,<ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M27nPfwgRmM</ref> King James<ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e9RfBi-F1GQ</ref>, Jay Polly<ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M27nPfwgRmM</ref> na Knowless<ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TRbiAat4sEc</ref>.Mu [[Umwana|abana]] be, '''Kankwanzi''' yemeza ko umuto [[umwana]] w’umukobwa witwa Umwali Aurore  ari we ugaragaza impano yo gukina ikinamico ndetse bakaba bakinana ari [[umwana]] we mu Urunana yitwa Kereri [Claire]<ref>http://isimbi.rw/imyidagaduro/article/menya-claire-umukobwa-wa-kankwanzi-mu-maraso-akaba-uwa-bushombe-mu-runana</ref>.Ashishikariza abakuru biyumvamo impano kudatinya kuzigaragaza ndetse akanasaba abandi bamaze kugira aho bagera muri uyu mwuga gushyigikira impano z’abakiri bato nk'[[Umwana|abana]].<ref>https://www.eachamps.rw/article/5604/Shira-amatsiko-kuri-Kankwanzi-ukinana-numukobwa-we-mu-Runana</ref><ref>http://isimbi.rw/imyidagaduro/article/menya-claire-umukobwa-wa-kankwanzi-mu-maraso-akaba-uwa-bushombe-mu-runana</ref>

